<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٧٤٩٢ - <span class="c2">«لا خير فيمن لا يضيف»</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
